  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\nIssue is reproducible when focus is set in input field with open keyboard (i.e. chat) and app is in foreground (so you don't manually switching off wi-fi to trigger it)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nKeyboard is closed, bottom sheet is visible\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n![photo_2020-04-21 17 51 54](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/79886544-60105580-83f9-11ea-87a0-31538706c518.jpeg)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status on wi-fi network\r\n- Join to any chat and set focus in input field\r\n- Go out from WI-FI zone to activate mobile connection (it is not reproducible if the change was triggered manually)\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: Release v1.3\r\n- Operating System: iOS, iPhone 7 \r\nI don't think it is platform specific, but don't have android with mobile connection to try it.\r\n@Serhy can you assist please? \r\n\r\n\r\n",
